 Step 7 - begin consensus

 Step 7.1 - choose speaker among delegates (validators)
device_1 is speaker: False
device_16 is speaker: True
device_9 is speaker: False
device_14 is speaker: False
device_8 is speaker: False
validator device_16 has been chosen as speaker for the consensus round 0

 Step 7.2 - build candidate block
device_16 - speaker hashing the block...
device_16 - speaker mines a block in 0.19133210182189941 seconds.

 Step 7.3 - propose it to delegates
validator device_16 is propagating its block to validator device_8.
validator device_8 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_16
validator device_16 is propagating its block to validator device_14.
validator device_14 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_16
validator device_16 is propagating its block to validator device_1.
validator device_1 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_16
validator device_16 is propagating its block to validator device_9.
validator device_9 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_16
accept block based on PoA
device_1 - delegate 1/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_16 mined by device_16 has been verified by device_1!
Delegate device_1 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_16.
accept block based on PoA
device_9 - delegate 2/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received

accept block based on PoA

accept block based on PoA

 Step 7 - begin consensus

 Step 7.1 - choose speaker among delegates (validators)
device_15 is speaker: False
device_10 is speaker: False
device_17 is speaker: False
device_12 is speaker: True
device_13 is speaker: False
validator device_12 has been chosen as speaker for the consensus round 0

 Step 7.2 - build candidate block
device_12 - speaker hashing the block...
device_12 - speaker mines a block in 0.1949000358581543 seconds.

 Step 7.3 - propose it to delegates
validator device_12 is propagating its block to validator device_13.
validator device_13 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_12

 Step 7 - begin consensus

 Step 7.1 - choose speaker among delegates (validators)
device_9 is speaker: True
device_10 is speaker: False
device_13 is speaker: False
device_16 is speaker: False
device_1 is speaker: False
validator device_9 has been chosen as speaker for the consensus round 0

 Step 7.2 - build candidate block
device_9 - speaker hashing the block...
device_9 - speaker mines a block in 0.19536447525024414 seconds.

 Step 7.3 - propose it to delegates
validator device_9 is propagating its block to validator device_16.
validator device_16 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_9
validator device_9 is propagating its block to validator device_13.
validator device_13 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_9
validator device_9 is propagating its block to validator device_1.
validator device_1 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_9
validator device_9 is propagating its block to validator device_10.
validator device_10 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_9
accept block based on PoA
device_10 - delegate 1/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_9 mined by device_9 has been verified by device_10!
Delegate device_10 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_9.
accept block based on PoA
device_13 - delegate 2/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_9 mined by device_9 has been verified by device_13!
Delegate device_13 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_9.
accept block based on PoA
device_16 - delegate 3/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_9 mined by device_9 has been verified by device_16!
Delegate device_16 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_9.
accept block based on PoA
device_1 - delegate 4/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_9 mined by device_9 has been verified by device_1!
Delegate device_1 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_9.
4/4 from delegates approved the candidate block
d_9 - v has appened a block to its chain. Chain length now - 21
delegate device_9 is requesting its associated workers to download the block it just added to its chain
